      <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.29350-15/451245138_1417367702306565_6458817057377601184_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=110&amp;ig_cache_key=MzQxMzMwODA2MzM4NzUxNDYyMw%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjEwODB4NjA3LnNkci5kZWZhdWx0X2ltYWdlLkMzIn0%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=aLR6THAQ2k8Q7kNvwH5Xdxq&amp;_nc_oc=AdrktNkYeFD_jJeTi9zlrsumjA7d7rT1yMBxCMrYJL9emX6Vid_2M351j9YG3LeUowc&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;se=7&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=yjSjmw0x0m9RMbsPzHu6Nw&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfyXC8boZBHgcLwrkdEOU71RfCbXNlxjYmcN6rkOktluyA&amp;oe=69CA3EC2" alt="Slide 1 fra @runebrink" style="max-width: 48%; margin: 0 1% 8px 0;" /><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.29350-15/451499584_469392666036992_6129616895425435764_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=103&amp;ig_cache_key=MzQxMzMwODA2MzExMDg1OTcwOA%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjc4N3g0NDIuc2RyLmRlZmF1bHRfaW1hZ2UuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=3YXuyXjJcYwQ7kNvwG2-Xq1&amp;_nc_oc=AdpQO7d9aLDVbP9JYFXF_2VcpglfhREdNKZxGUIuQqSGqgqkluDjF0yRgEBlxuregIQ&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=yjSjmw0x0m9RMbsPzHu6Nw&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfyMLrJ_4vZW4SCqYJNtGPQF4dLgNKMkChdjQHjyydcH_w&amp;oe=69CA3FB2" alt="Slide 2 fra @runebrink" style="max-width: 48%; margin: 0 1% 8px 0;" /><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/623972297_1431214018593440_5897953356135117109_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_s360x360_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=108&amp;ig_cache_key=MzQxMzMwMjUxODgyODE1MzYxNw%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjcyMHg0MDQuc2RyLkMzIn0%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=khBNqGXjW9IQ7kNvwHYxr-h&amp;_nc_oc=AdpMJ7umRXIr7Af9eLfc_JEQg0P0X2ZsOiARhgABIiNOSs01xqG28WRFeu2oqQ8uPGQ&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=yjSjmw0x0m9RMbsPzHu6Nw&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfyZY4aTh7PGjbOSVDHXo7Wi0DkYi2RaxNYrt4W_5Mui6A&amp;oe=69CA3553" alt="Slide 3 fra @runebrink" style="max-width: 48%; margin: 0 1% 8px 0;" /><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/654184814_18089740523181643_4090737397953343787_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=107&amp;ig_cache_key=MzQxMzMwODA2MzEwMjM4ODYxNQ%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjg0Nng0Nzcuc2RyLkMzIn0%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=Hy6W36JTY5YQ7kNvwFd8EUU&amp;_nc_oc=AdpORH5-WHUr-typdS_ibWDCq6pS2mCA7K8sqPdKJTuvVeGPYFtdkhcL2gjdCduwojQ&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;se=8&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=yjSjmw0x0m9RMbsPzHu6Nw&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_Afwr8THVw0gXN4-sVGSdnnYzTEmDQukx3qA3Eb_eXYf3Mw&amp;oe=69CA2C28" alt="Slide 4 fra @runebrink" style="max-width: 48%; margin: 0 1% 8px 0;" /></p><p><strong>🖼️ Slideshow (7 medier)</strong></p><p><strong>@runebrink</strong></p><p>If you visit the castle ruin of #hammershus on #bornholm this summer, I recommend the visitor center, where I helped @yokecph design the exhibition about the history of the castle. Based on drone 3D scans of the castle ruin, you can watch a 12 meter wide video projection experience, flying trough the castle and down into the dungeons as they might have looked. You can also interact with the castle yourself and read about all the scary locations of torture and oppression as the castle was called “Castle of hatred” by the local people. All illustrations are also based on 3D scans of real humans. Designed for @museumsydoestdanmark and @naturstyrelsen 2018</p><p><a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/C9egZwEsfPr/">Se slideshow på Instagram</a></p>]]></description>
